          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-947B86L6-line-1" n="1">You always are making a God of your Spouse,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-947B86L6-line-2" n="2">But this neither Reason nor Conscience allows;<lb/>But·this·neither·Reason·nor·Conscience·allows;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-947B86L6-line-3" n="3">Perhaps, you will say, 'tis in gratitude due,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-947B86L6-line-4" n="4">And you adore him because he adores you,<lb/>And·you·adore·him,·because·he·adores·you,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-947B86L6-line-5" n="5">Your Argument's weak, and so you will find,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-947B86L6-line-6" n="6">For you by this Rule, must adore all mankind,<lb/>For·you·by·this·Rule,·must·adore· all·mankind.</l>
          </lg>
